      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like you're being a bit evasive. if the \"negative impacts\" are mostly just theoretical or small, then isn't the whole \"economic burden\" argument basically just a myth used by politicians? seems like the benefits are pretty much settled science whereas the downsides are just people worrying about things that don't actually happen.",
