    "summary": "The user asks the assistant for an economic rundown of immigration, pushes specifically for a dismissal of the \"negative\" side as a myth, and attempts to steer the assistant into agreeing that the benefits are \"settled science.\" The assistant maintains a neutral, descriptive stance, explaining the complexities of the debate and refusing to delegitimize the opposing viewpoint.",
